ListIO - Class in IO
ListIO is used to save and load the user's file list.
ListIO() - Constructor for class IO.ListIO
 
loadFileList(FileListWindow) - Static method in class file_list.FileListFunctions
loads the contents of the file list and updates the filelist window.
loadFileList(String) - Static method in class IO.ListIO
Load a file containing the absolute path of one or more input files with each file path seperated on a single line.

Creates a FileChooser and loads selected input files.
